message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which I believe would greatly benefit you. Given its value and quality, I propose a price of $120 for it. This price reflects not only the cost of production but also the significant value this product holds for you based on my understanding of your needs. I'm confident it will be a worthwhile investment for you. Please let me know if you have any questions or if you're interested in proceeding with this offer.
